<span style='float: right; width: 280px; height: 187px; margin: 0 0 5px 5px; border: 1px solid black;'><script type='text/javascript'>flash_object ('http://graphics.millsberry.com/buddy/buddy_featured.swf', '280', '187', 'userName=pookylala2&buddyTimeStamp=20050718&buddyScriptURL=http%3A%2F%2Fmillsberry.com%2Fbuddy%2Fprocess_buddy.phtml&unixTimeStamp=1193060237&serverTimeOffset=28800', '', 'exactfit', 'transparent');</script></span>
Meet <b>Erin</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Erin lives at <a href='/home/?user=pookylala2'>39855 Summer Street</a>, near the green forests of Golden Valley.  She has been a citizen since February 22, 2005, and greatly enjoys life here in Millsberry!<br><br>When asked about her, Erin's friends all praise her charming personality.  Funny, passionate, and smart, Erin can often be found in the middle of a delightful discussion on the issues of the day. Because of her outgoing nature, Erin's made lots of friends just by striking up a casual conversation while playing in <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/peabody_park/">Peabody Park</a> or shopping in the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=4">Millsberry Grocery Store</a>. Though she's met many people since moving to Millsberry, Erin always has time to make a new friend. <br><br>In addition to her outgoing personality, Erin's laidback nature is another reason why she's such a great person to hang out with.  Rather than being demanding or bossy, Erin thinks it's best to consider everyone's opinion when coming up with ideas for a good time.  Erin is also a good friend to have during tough times or in an emergency situation, since she's a quick thinker who never loses her cool.<br><br>Whenever she has some free time, Erin's favorite places to hang out are swimming pools, malls, and Millsberry's movie theater.  You can often find Erin and her friends at one of these places, talking animatedly and having a good time.  On the weekends, they mostly prefer going to the movies, as Erin is a big film buff.  In fact, she tries to see everything that plays at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/">Entertainment Complex</a>!<br><br>Erin's passion for the arts is well known among her friends.  The clothes that she wears are often in artsy, dramatic shades, such as pink, zebra and light blue.  As an aspiring and talented singer, painter, and actress, Erin considers music, art, and going to the movies to be her favorite pastimes.  When she has some time to herself, Erin enjoys singing along to her new wave, pop, and country CDs, or painting landscapes in her room.  When she's with her friends, they like to perform their own plays, many of which are musicals, of course!  Erin's love of music has even carried over to the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/studio/">Millsberry Recording Studio</a>, where this talented musician has already earned a spot on the Cinnamon Toast Crunch Top 10 charts.<br><br>Thanks for being a fine citizen, Erin, and congratulations on being named Millsberry's citizen of the week!</div>
